.refresh.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h2 class=\"greylarge\">Lasting Hair Removal</h2>\n<a href=\"hair/lasting-hair-removal\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/banner.removal.jpg\" /></a></div>\n',NULL),(107,22,'postMenuLabel','id','Aesthetic Center',NULL),(108,22,'postMenuLabel','en','Aesthetic Center',NULL),(109,23,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | ACNE CLEAR LASER (eMax Laser)</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\">&nbsp;\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"acne-care-plus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Acne Clean Laser</h2>\n\n<p><strong><span>Menghilangkan noda gelap dan warna kemerahan karena jerawat untuk kulit yang bercahaya </span></strong><br />\nPerawatan ini menggunakan energi laser <em>Intense Pulse Light</em> yang bekerja dengan aman dan langsung menyerap pigmen sel yang menghitam melalui penyaringan sinar UV. Selama sesi penyinaran laser, Anda hanya akan merasakan sedikit sensasi cubitan dan rasa hangat di wajah; sehingga tidak dibutuhkan pemberian bius lokal. Setelah menjalani 4-6 sesi perawatan Acne Clear Laser, kemerahan dan noda gelap akan berkurang secara nyata, digantikan oleh kulit yang lebih halus dan bersih.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span>Hasilnya</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Mengurangi peradangan pada jerawat</li>\n	<li>Mengurangi kelenjar minyak penyebab jerawat</li>\n	<li>Membersihkan pori-pori yang tersumbat</li>\n	<li>Mengurangi kemerahan dan noda gelap akibat jerawat</li>\n	<li>Merangsang pembentukan kolagen untuk menciptakan sel-sel kulit yang lebih kuat</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span>PERAWATAN SETELAHNYA:</span></strong> Sejumlah perawatan harus dilakukan dengan teratur, dengan penggunaan produk perawatan wajah dan tabir surya.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(110,23,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | ACNE CLEAR LASER (eMax Laser)</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.acne01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"acne-care-plus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Acne Clean Laser</h2>\n\n<p><strong><span>Clear dark spots and acne redness for a luminous skin result </span></strong><br />\nThe treatment involves using Intense Pulse Light laser energy that safely and directly absorb discolored cell pigments through the UV light filtration. During the laser session, you will feel no severe pain but a slight pinch and warmth on the face; therefore local anesthetic is not needed. After 4-6 sessions of Acne Clear Laser, redness and dark spots will be noticeably reduced, revealing a smoother and clearer skin.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span>The results</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Calm inflamed pimples</li>\n	<li>Reduce sebaceous glands which cause acne</li>\n	<li>Clear clogged pores</li>\n	<li>Reduce redness and dark spots from acne</li>\n	<li>Stimulate collagen to develop stronger skin cells</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span>AFTER TREATMENT:</span></strong> A certain amount of nurturing and treatment should be done consistently, with a regular use of skincare products and sunscreen.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(111,23,'postMenuLabel','id','Skin',NULL),(112,23,'postMenuLabel','en','Skin',NULL),(113,24,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"top\">\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Derma Frax (Firexel Laser)</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end #top-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.dermafrax01.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"picNav\">\r\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"pore-skin-stem-rejuvenation\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"right-460\">\r\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Derma Frax</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Change the skin entirely, clean up old cells, smoothen the skin after only one treatment.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <span class=\"ijo2\">Fraxional Laser</span> treatment is an advanced anti-aging innovation that is approved by the Food and Drug Administration of USA. Many small, accurate laser beams can be adjusted to give the appropriate depth of treatment, depending on skin condition. The principle of <span class=\"ijo2\">Fraxional Laser</span> is to treat the skin at the mildest degree to stimulate deep skin cell remodeling and neocollagenesis in the dermis. The skin cells are remodeled entirely without any damage to the upper skin layer or nearby tissues. This laser is indicated for uneven skin tone, diffuse redness, spots from acne, acne scars or even deep melasma and large pores. The skin will look smoother and brighter after only one treatment and the result lasts for 6 months as skin cells keep working continually. The treatment has high safety and does not take a long time to perform. Also, the treatment requires no downtime so the patients can continue their daily life activities immediately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Treatment :</span></strong> While treating, the patients will feel warm on the treated area. The treatment is scheduled once a month for 4-6 sessions to ensure permanent results.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Improve acne scar and deep melasma</li>\r\n	<li>Decrease pore size and smoothen the facial skin</li>\r\n	<li>Stimulate new collagen in the dermis for stronger skin</li>\r\n	<li>Visible result after just one session and 6-month long lasting</li>\r\n	<li>No downtime</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Post treatment :</span></strong> The patients should frequently and continually apply intensive moisturizer and sun block with SPF 30 or more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Treatment :</span></strong> While treating, the patients will feel warm on the treated area. The treatment is scheduled once a month for 4-6 sessions to ensure permanent results.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Improve acne scar and deep melasma</li>\r\n	<li>Decrease pore size and smoothen the facial skin</li>\r\n	<li>Stimulate new collagen in the dermis for stronger skin</li>\r\n	<li>Visible result after just one session and 6-month long lasting</li>\r\n	<li>No downtime</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n',NULL),(114,24,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"top\">\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Derma Frax (Firexel Laser)</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end #top-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.dermafrax01.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"picNav\">\r\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"pore-skin-stem-reju