lass=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Melanin Block</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.melaninblock01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"super-anti-oxidant\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"birthmark\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Melanin Block</h2>\n\n<p>Age spots and freckles are caused by skin pigmentation that resides in the epidermis and causes excessive amounts of melanin production. Injecting melanin block in affected areas will help prevent hyperpigmentation of the skin and reduce blemishes, dark spots, age spots, and freckles. Liposome, which is a natural extract, makes up for the aging collagen and restore strength to your skin.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(167,37,'postMenuLabel','id','Melanin Block',NULL),(168,37,'postMenuLabel','en','Melanin Block',NULL),(169,38,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Birth Marks / Redness /Tattoo Removel</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.birthmark01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"melanin-block\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"dual-yellow\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Birth Marks / Redness /Tattoo Removel</h2>\n\n<p>Perawatan ini menghilangkan tanda lahir, flek hitam, bercak hitam karena penuaan, bekas luka dan tato dengan menghancurkan sel-sel melanin menjadi partikel-partikel sehingga berangsur-angsur menghilang. Ada dua jenis sinar laser yang digunakan pada perawatan ini, yaitu laser dengan panjang gelombang 1064 mm dan 532 mm. Jenis sinar yang pertama digunakan untuk menyingkirkan tato berwarna merah dan biru, tanda lahir hitam, dan flek hitam membandel karena sinar matahari. Jenis sinar yang kedua digunakan untuk menghilangkan kemerahan, tanda lahir merah, flek hitam samar karena sinar matahari dengan melepaskan gelombang frekuensi ke area yang dituju. Panas yang dihasilkan akan menghancurkan melanin atau tato. Setelah itu, sel-sel darah putih di dalam tubuh akan menyerap melanin dan berangsur-angsur menghilangkannya. Biasanya, jumlah sesi perawatan yang harus dilakukan bergantung pada dalamnya pigmentasi dan banyaknya area kulit yang terpengaruh atau pada perawatan yang harus dijalani setelahnya. Berikut ini adalah masalah-masalah kulit yang dapat ditangani:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Flek hitam karena sinar matahari dan flek hitam pada tulang pipi</li>\n	<li>Tato</li>\n	<li>Bibir yang menggelap</li>\n	<li>Tanda lahir merah dan hitam</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n',NULL),(170,38,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Birth Marks / Redness /Tattoo Removel</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.birthmark01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"melanin-block\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"dual-yellow\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Birth Marks / Redness /Tattoo Removel</h2>\n\n<p>This treatment gets rid of birth marks, freckles, age spots, scars, and tattoos by destroying melanin cells into particles until they fade away. There are two types of laser that are employed in this treatment, with the wavelength 1064 mm and 532 mm respectively. The former uses to get rid of black and blue tattoos, black birth marks, and stubborn sun freckles. The latter uses to remove redness, red birth marks, faint sun freckles by releasing frequency wavelengths to the pigmented lesions. The heat will destroy the melanin or tattoos. After that the white blood cells in the body will absorb the melanin and fade them away. Typically, the number of treatments depends on the depth of the pigmentation and the amount of skin pigmentations in the skin or the maintenance of your skin after the treatment. The following skin problems can be treated:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Sun freckles and freckles on cheekbones</li>\n	<li>Tattoos</li>\n	<li>Darkened lips</li>\n	<li>Red and black birthmarks</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n',NULL),(171,38,'postMenuLabel','id','Birth Marks / Redness /Tattoo Removel',NULL),(172,38,'postMenuLabel','en','Birth Marks / Redness /Tattoo Removel',NULL),(173,39,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Dual Yellow</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.dualyellow01.jpg\