left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"turn-of-the-century\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"lifting-original3d\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Face Tite</h2>\n\n<p class=\"big\">Rekonstruksi Wajah Tanpa Operasi</p>\n\n<p><strong>Kembalikan kekencangan kulit remaja Anda dengan metode tanpa operasi</strong></p>\n\n<h2>FACE TITE adalah jawabannya</h2>\n\n<p><em>Face Tite</em> adalah inovasi baru yang dapat membuat wajah Anda tampak lebih ramping dengan kulit yang halus, kencang, dan tampak lebih muda. Perawatan ini dapat dengan mudah menyelesaikan semua masalah kulit, mengurangi minyak berlebih dan menciptakan ukuran wajah yang sempurna dengan memperbaiki bentuk wajah, alis, dahi dan sudut mata.</p>\n\n<h3>PRINSIP-PRINSIP DAN PROSES PERAWATAN</h3>\n\n<p><em>Face Tite</em> adalah teknologi yang menggunakan radiofrekuensi (RF) untuk mengencangkan kulit di sekitar mata, wajah, leher dan bagian tubuh lainnya. Efek pengencangan ini terjadi pada area berlemak tepat di bawah permukaan kulit dengan menggunakan elektroda internal dan eksternal. Energi yang dihasilkan oleh radiofrekuensi ini menciptakan panas di antara kedua elektroda, yang pada akhirnya menghancurkan lemak dan merangsang pertumbuhan kolagen di dalam kulit. Produksi kolagen akan membuat kulit Anda semakin lentur, bervolume dan kencang, serta mengurangi kerutan dan garis-garis di bagian-bagian tubuh yang berbeda. Hasil positif ini terjadi karena elektroda internal <em>Blunt</em>, yang dirancang untuk tidak mempengaruhi area di sekitarnya. <em>Face Tite</em> biasa digunakan untuk merawat kelopak mata bagian bawah, pipi, garis senyum, bibir atas, garis rahang, garis dahi. Perawatan ini juga bisa dilakukan di bagian tubuh yang menjadi menggelambir seperti area diatas pusar, paha bagian dalam atau lengan bagian atas</p>\n\n<p><em>Face Tite</em> memberikan sejumlah keuntungan pada pasien. Hal ini terjadi karena mereka dapat melihat hasil yang nyata tanpa menjalani operasi. Proses <em>face tite</em> tidak memerlukan sayatan sehingga pasien tidak perlu menginap di rumah sakit.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Hasil yang didapat</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Wajah yang lebih ramping</li>\n	<li>Keriput yang berkurang</li>\n	<li>Kulit yang lebih halus</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Hasil perawatan <em>FACE TITE</em> bertahan paling sedikit selama tiga tahun (semi-permanen). Efeknya 80% sama dengan efek yang didapat dari operasi <em>facelift.</em> Pasien dapat menjalani <em>face tite</em> berulang kali, tidak seperti metode operasi yang bisa menimbulkan kerusakan syaraf bila dilakukan untuk kedua kalinya.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Bagaimana Face Tite berbeda dari Thread Lifting?</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Dua kali lebih efektif dibandingkan <em>thread lifting</em></li>\n	<li>Bertahan lebih lama daripada <em>thread lifting</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Calon pasien yang sesuai</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Berusia antara 30-65 tahun (memberikan efek yang sangat efektif)</li>\n	<li>Pasien yang memiliki lemak berlebih di bawah mata dan pipi; patient dengan kulit kendur</li>\n	<li>Pasien yang ingin menghindari resiko operasi</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Waktu yang dibutuhkan sampai hasilnya terlihat</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>Para pasien dapat melihat hasilnya langsung setelah perawatan. Efeknya akan terlihat maksimal setelah 6-12 minggu.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Perawatan setelahnya</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>Pasien dapat langsung pulang dan kembali melakukan kegiatan seperti biasa.</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite02.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"logoHair\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.surgeons.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(214,49,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Face Tite (NON-Surgical Facial Reconstruction)</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"turn-of-the-century\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"lifting-original3d\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Face Tite</h2>\n\n<p class=\"big\">NON-Surgical Facial Reconstruction</p>\n\n<p><strong>Lift aging face to its youthful firmness with non-surgical method</strong></p>\n\n<h2>FACE TITE is the answer</h2>\n\n<p>Face Tite is a new innovation that can make your face appear leaner with a smooth, firm and younger-looking skin. The treatment effortlessly solves all facial skin problems, reduce excessive sebum and create a perfect face dimension by repositioning face shape, eyebrows, forehead and eyes&#39; corner.</p>\n\n<h3>THE PRINCIPLES AND TREATMENT PROCESS</h3>\n\n<p>Face Tite is a technology derived from Radio Frequency (RF) to firm the skin around the eyes, face, neck and other parts of the body. The tightening effect occurs in the fatty areas just under the skin surface by using the External Electrode and the Internal Electrode. Using the energy from this radio frequency creates heat between the two electrodes, which break down the fat and stimulate the development of collagen in the skin. The production of collagen makes your skin become more flexible, voluminous and firmer, as well as reduce wrinkles and lines in different areas. The positive results are due to the Blunt internal electrode, which is carefully designed to not affect the surrounding normal area. Face Tite is commonly used to treat lower eyelid, cheeks, nasolabial folds, upper lip, jawline and forehead lines. The treatment can also be applied on specific areas of the body that becomes jowly through time such as the area above the belly button, inner thigh, or upper arms.</p>\n\n<p>Face Tite gives numbers of benefits to the patients. This is mainly because they can see a visible result without undergoing a surgery. The process requires is no invasive process and therefore there is no need to stay at the hospital.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">The results</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Slimmer face</li>\n	<li>Less wrinkles</li>\n	<li>Smoother skin</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The result of using FACE TITE lasts at least three years (Semi-Permanent). The effect is 80% the same as normal surgical facelift. Patients can undergo Face Tite as many times they like, unlike the surgical method that may cause nerve damage if processed for the second time.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">How is Face Tite different from Thread Lifting? </span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Twice as effective as thread lifting</li>\n	<li>Require more downtime than thread lifting.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Suitable candidates</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Age between 30-65 (give highly effective result)</li>\n	<li>Patients with excess fat layers under eyes and cheeks; patients with sagging skin</li>\n	<li>Patients who avoid surgical risks</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Time needed to show result</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>Patients can see a visible result immediately after the treatment. The effect provides the maximum result between 6 - 12 weeks.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Post-treatment</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>Patients are able to go home and get back to normal daily routine right away</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite02.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"logoHair\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.surgeons.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(215,49,'postMenuLabel','id','Face Tite',NULL),(216,49,'postMenuLabel','en','Face Tite',NULL),(217,50,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Fine Thread</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.finethread01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"face-tite\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"skin-lifting-botox\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">3D Original Ultra V Lift</h2>\n\n<p><em>3D Original Ultra V Lift</em> adalah perawatan tanpa operasi yang menjawab kebutuhan Anda dalam memperbaiki kulit yang mengendur dan garis rahang yang tidak rata. Perawatan ini menggunakan benang PDO (Polidioxanone ) yang dapat diserap untuk memperbaiki garis rahang menjadi bentuk V, sekaligus mengangkat dan menyesuaikan bagian-bagian yang diinginkan seperti pipi, dagu, hidung, alis, dan sudut luar mata menjadi lebih sempurna.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Jenis benang</span></strong><br />\nBenang 3D UVL jenis PDO (Polydioxanone) yang dapat diserap, dua kali lebih tebal dan panjang dibandingkan benang biasa. Benang ini telah berstandar CE di Eropa, Korea dan Thailand.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Prosedur</span></strong><br />\n<em>3D Original Ultra V Lift</em> dilakukan dengan memasukkan benang halus yang dapat diserap ke bawah jaringan subkutan atau hipodermis dimana kaitnya yang sangat halus mengikat dan merangsang pembentukan kolagen pada epidermis, sehingga kulit yang mengendur dapat kembali kencang. Anda dapat langsung melihat hasilnya setelah melakukan perawatan ini dalam 2 - 6 minggu. Benang yang digunakan akan hilang dengan sendirinya, sehingga menjamin keamanan tingkat tinggi dan efek samping yang minimal.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Perawatan setelahnya</span></strong><br />\nMiliki wajah dengan bentuk V dengan kontur yang lebih halus dan dengan kerutan atau bahkan garis-garis halus di bawah mata yang lebih sedikit. <em>3D Original Ultra V Lift</em> membantu menciptakan dimensi baru dari penampilan Anda, membantu pembentukan kolagen dan mencerahkan kulit dengan prosedur tanpa operasi. Perawatan ini dilakukan dalam waktu yang singkat dan Anda dalam kembali beraktivitas setelahnya.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Mengapa Dermaster 3D Original Ultra V Lift (Thread lifting) Lebih Baik?</span></strong><br />\nDi Dermaster, kami menggunakan suatu teknik <em>&ldquo;parallel vector&rdquo;</em> yang unik dan canggih didukung dengan tim ahli kulit kami yang berpengalaman. Pada perawatan ini, benang dimasukkan dengan hati-hati ke dalam lapisan kulit yang berbeda-beda dan masuk ke jaringan kulit melalui saluran yang berbentuk seperti <em>parallel vector</em>. Hasilnya bertahan lebih lama dibandingkan dengan teknik biasa; hasilnya juga menampilkan garis rahang yang alami disertai dengan kulit yang halus dan kencang.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(218,50,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Fine Thread</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.finethread01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"face-tite\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"skin-lifting-botox\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">3D Original Ultra V Lift</h2>\n\n<p>3D Original Ultra V Lift is a non-surgical treatment that answers the need to fix loose, sagging skin and undefined jawline. He used an absorbable PDO thread (Polidioxanone thread) to reposition jawline to a V shape and simultaneously lift and adjust desirable areas such as cheek, chin, nose, eyebrow, and outer corner of the eye to their perfect position.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Thread type</span></strong><br />\nName 3D UVL absorbable thread type PDO (Polydioxanone) a Twin-Fold thicker and longer than normal thread. Received the CE standard in Europe, Korea and Thai</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Procedures</span></strong><br />\n3D Original Ultra V Lift involves the insertion of a fine absorbable thread into underlying subcutaneous tissues where its microfine barbs anchor and stimulate collagen production in epidermis, gathering sagging skin and restoring its elasticity. You can see an immediate visible result after the process and experience a clearly defined face within 2 - 6 weeks. The thread is dissolves over time, ensuring a high safety and minimal side effect.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Post-treatment</span></strong><br />\nExperience a defined V-Shape face with smoother contours and less wrinkles or even fine lines under eyes. 3D Original Ultra V Lift helps create a new dimension of your appearance, promote collagen production and brighten the skin with non-surgery procedure. The treatment requires no significant downtime and patients can get back to daily routine after the process.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Why is Dermaster 3D Original Ultra V Lift (Thread lifting) better than others?</span></strong><br />\nAt Dermaster, we perform a unique and sophisticated &quot;parallel vector&quot; technique which requires a lengthy experience from our dermatologist team. With this approach, the threads are carefully inserted into different skin layers and are sophisticatedly led into tissue via parallel-vector-like tunnel under the distance Control Technique. The result lasts longer than normal technique and gives you a naturally defined jawline with smooth and firm skin.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(219,50,'postMenuLabel','id','3D Original Ultra V Lift',NULL),(220,50,'postMenuLabel','en','3D Original Ultra V Lift',NULL),(221,51,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Skin Lifting Botox</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.skinlifting01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"lifting-original3d\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Skin Lifting Botox</h2>\n\n<p><em>Skin Lifting Botox</em> merupakan teknik yang terbaru dan unik, yang dirancang khusus untuk merawat keriput dan lipatan-lipatan halus. Dibawah pengawasan para ahli kulit, sejumlah kecil Botox diinjeksikan ke dalam garis otot secara akurat, sehingga tidak ada resiko yang menyebabkan peregangan pada bagian wajah yang lain. Terapi <em>Skin Lifting Botox</em> bekerja pada sebagian kecil otot dan pada lapisan kulit yang lebih dalam. Oleh karena itu, pasien tidak akan merasakan efek yang tidak alami pada wajah.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Keuntungan</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Tidak ada efek samping yang mempengaruhi ekspresi wajah</li>\n	<li>Tidak ada sensasi tegang pada wajah; menyingkirkan garis-garis halus dan kerutan pada wajah</li>\n	<li>Menyempurnakan bentuk wajah secara alami</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(222,51,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Skin Lifting Botox</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.skinlifting01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"lifting-original3d\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Skin Lifting Botox</h2>\n\n<p>Skin Lifting Botox an advance and unique technique specially designed to treat wrinkles and MicroVolume folds. Under dermatologist&#39;s care, very small amount of Botox are precisely injected into specific muscle lines, eliminating the risk to cause unnatural stretch or restrain on other facial spots. Skin Lifting Botox therapy targets specific small muscles and let the treatment works down to the lower skin layer. Therefore, patients would never experience a fake plastic feeling or unemotional face.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Advantage</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Cause no effect to the ability to form facial expressions</li>\n	<li>Eliminate over-stretching sensation on face; flat out fine lines and wrinkles on face</li>\n	<li>Naturally lift your face to a perfect balance.</li>\n</ul>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/symbol05.gif\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(223,51,'postMenuLabel','id','Skin Lifting Botox',NULL),(224,51,'postMenuLabel','en','Skin Lifting Botox',NULL),(225,52,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Therma CPT plus</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.therma01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"face-tite\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.therma.jpg\" /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/vH6hQ1Veo0k\" width=\"460\"></iframe></div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Therma CPT plus</h2>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Apakah Perawatan Therma CPT plus itu?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus adalah suatu perawatan yang aman, tanpa operasi, bekerja dengan radiofrekuensi (RF) yang telah terbukti secara klinis dalam menghaluskan, mengencangkan dan membentuk kulit untuk penampilan yang terlihat lebih muda. Perawatan ini memberikan hasil yang alami dan tahan lama pada semua jenis kulit - semuanya Anda dapatkan dalam satu jenis perawatan.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Apakah Therma CPT plus itu?</span></strong><br />\nCPT adalah <em>Comfort Pulse Technology.</em> Pada dasarnya, CPT telah terbukti efektif saat digunakan pada Therma CPT plus &ndash; satu-satunya alat yang menggunakan monopolar, energi gabungan radiofrekuensi untuk mengencangkan kulit. Akan tetapi, CPT bekerja lebih baik dengan pengguna yang terintegrasi dan fitur kenyamanan pasien untuk memberikan hasil dan pengalaman yang terbaik.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Bagian tubuh mana saja yang bisa dirawat dengan Therma CPT plus?</span></strong><br />\nProsedur Therma CPT plus dapat secara efektif dan aman merawat kulit di hampir semua bagian tubuh, termasuk wajah, mata, bibir, perut, tangan, lengan, paha dan pantat. Therma CPT plus juga dapat mengurangi selulit untuk sementara.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Kondisi apa saja yang bisa dirawat dengan Therma CPT plus?</span></strong><br />\nPada bagian wajah, Therma CPT plus dapat merawat keriput dan garis-garis halus, kulit yang turun, mengendurnya kulit di bawah dagu, ketidaksempurnaan garis rahang, mengendurnya kulit leher (&ldquo;leher kalkun&rdquo;), dan ketidaksempurnaan pada bibir. Pada area mata, Therma CPT plus dapat merawat kantung mata, <em>hooding</em> (kulit yang turun pada kelopak mata atas), tekstur kasar pada kelopak mata, dan kondisi lain yang membuat mata tampak lelah. Di bagian tubuh lainnya, Therma CPT plus dapat merawat kulit keriput, crepey, kendur atau tekstur kulit yang tidak rata.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Dimana saya bisa memperoleh perawatan Therma CPT plus?</span></strong><br />\nDokter di seluruh dunia menawarkan perawatan Therma CPT plus. Untuk menemukan praktisi Therma CPT plus di dekat tempat tinggal Anda, gunakan fitur &ldquo;Find a Doctor&rdquo; pada di situs ini.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Berapa kali perawatan yang saya butuhkan?</span></strong><br />\nTidak seperti prosedur lainnya, Therma CPT plus sudah memperlihatkan hasil pada sebagian besar pasien dalam satu kali perawatan. Sebenarnya, dalam hal pengencangan dan pembentukan kulit yang tahan lama, Therma CPT plus adalah satu-satunya perawatan yang ada.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Berapa lama waktu yang dibutuhkan untuk satu kali perawatan?</span></strong><br />\nPerawatan Therma CPT plus berlangsung sekitar 45 menit pada wajah dan sekitar 90 menit pada bagian tubuh lainnya, bergantung pada ukuran, lokasi dan kondisi bagian yang akan menjalani perawatan. Karena Therma CPT plus adalah prosedur yang singkat, maka perawatan ini cocok untuk gaya hidup Anda yang sibuk.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Adakah persiapan khusus sebelumnya atau prosedur tambahan setelahnya?</span></strong><br />\nTidak. Tidak seperti operasi, tidak diperlukan persiapan sebelum menjalani perawatan, seperti tes darah atau puasa. Dan tidak ada perawatan khusus setelahnya, selain perawatan dasar kulit dan pemakaian tabir surya sebagai bagian dari prosedur perawatan kulit. Karena perawatan Therma CPT plus tanpa efek samping, sebagian besar pasien dapat langsung kembali melakukan kegiatan seperti biasa setelah menjalani perawatan. Beberapa pasien mengalami kemerah-merahan sementara atau sedikit bengkak setelah menjalani perawatan, tetapi kondisi ini biasanya akan menghilang dalam waktu 24 jam.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Bagaimana perawatan Therma CPT plus bekerja?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus menggunakan teknologi radiofrekuensi untuk memanaskan lapisan kulit bagian dalam yang kaya kolagen. Proses pemanasan ini membantu untuk memadatkan kolagen yang ada dan merangsang pembentukan kolagen yang baru, sehingga mengurangi kulit kendur, memperbarui bentuknya, dan meningkatkan kehalusan dan tekstur pada permukaan kulit.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Apa yang membuat teknologi Therma CPT plus berbeda dengan prosedur pengencangan kulit lainnya? </span></strong><br />\nTidak seperti beberapa prosedur lainnya, Therma CPT plus dilakukan tanpa operasi, suntikan dan tanpa efek samping, dan Therma CPT plus bekerja di semua jenis kulit, baik kulit wajah atau kulit bagian tubuh lainnya. Prosedur lain yang menggunakan perawatan laser dan prosedur radiofrekuensi juga dapat mengencangkan kulit, tetapi tidak ada perawatan yang menggunakan panas sedalam Therma CPT plus. Dengan memanaskan lapisan kulit terdalam, Therma CPT plus bekerja paling efektif dalam memadatkan kolagen dan merangsang pembentukan kolagen yang baru, sehingga menghasilkan kulit yang lebih kencang dan penampilan lebih muda yang menyeluruh.</p>\n\n<h3>Therma CPT plus vs. Perawatan lainnya</h3>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Bagaimana hasil Therma CPT plus dibandingkan dengan perawatan lainnya? </span></strong><br />\nBeberapa orang menginginkan hasil operasi yang dramatis, sedangkan yang lainnya menginginkan perawatan dengan hasil yang lebih halus dan bertahap tanpa operasi serta tahan lama. Inilah dimana Therma CPT plus berhasil dalam memperbaiki warna, tekstur, dan kekencangan kulit. Saat losion dan obat-obatan tidaklah cukup dan operasi terlalu terlalu berlebihan, maka Therma CPT plus adalah solusi yang aman dan efektif.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Kapan hasilnya terlihat, dan bisa tahan berapa lama?</span></strong><br />\nHasilnya bisa langsung terlihat, dan bisa juga terlihat secara bertahap seiring dengan proses pembentukan kolagen. Bagi sebagian besar pasien, hasil pengencangan dan pembentukan wajah terlihat secara bertahap dalam dua hingga enam bulan setelah satu sesi perawatan. Hasilnya dapat tahan selama bertahun-tahun tergantung pada kondisi kulit Anda dan proses penuaan.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Apakah yang dirasakan saat menjalani perawatan Therma CPT plus?</span></strong><br />\nSetiap kali alat yang digunakan menyentuh kulit Anda, Anda akan merasakan sensasi dingin yang singkat, diikuti dengan sensasi panas yang mendalam tetapi singkat, kemudian diikuti dengan sensasi dingin lainnya. Sensasi panas adalah tanda bahwa lapisan kulit bagian dalam sedang dalam suhu yang efektif untuk proses pengencangan kulit. Jika dokter Anda mempunyai teknologi Therma CPT plus yang terbaru, Anda juga akan merasakan sensasi getaran lembut untuk menambah kenyamanan pasien. Selama prosedur berlangsung, dokter Anda akan menanyakan feedback mengenai tingkatan sensasi panas agar bisa disesuaikan dengan kenyamanan Anda dengan hasil yang maksimum.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Indikasi apa saja yang dimiliki oleh Therma CPT plus?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus diindikasikan untuk perawatan keriput dan pengurangan selulit untuk sementara tanpa operasi. Selain itu, Therma CPT plus merupakan sistem yang pertama dan satu-satunya yang mendapatkan ijin dari FDA untuk perawatan kelopak mata tanpa operasi.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(226,52,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Therma CPT plus</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.therma01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"face-tite\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.therma.jpg\" /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/vH6hQ1Veo0k\" width=\"460\"></iframe></div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Therma CPT plus</h2>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">What is the Therma CPT plus procedure?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus is a safe, non-invasive, radiofrequency (RF) cosmetic procedure that&#39;s clinically proven to help smooth, tighten and contour skin for an overall younger looking appearance. The treatment delivers natural looking results with little to no downtime on all skin types on and off the face, all in a single procedure.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">What is Therma CPT plus?</span></strong><br />\nCPT is Comfort Pulse Technology. At its core, CPT builds on the proven efficacy of the Therma CPT plus platform - the only device to use monopolar, capacitively coupled radiofrequency energy to tighten skin. But CPT goes a step further with integrated user and patient comfort features to deliver the best results AND the best treatment experience.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">What parts of the body does Therma CPT plus treat? </span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus procedures can effectively and safely treat skin on most body parts, including the face, eyes, lips, tummy, arms, hands, thighs and buttocks. Therma CPT plus can also temporarily reduce the appearance of cellulite.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">What conditions does Therma CPT plus treat?</span></strong><br />\nOn the face, Therma CPT plus can treat wrinkles and fine lines, sagging skin, loose jowls, lack of definition in the jaw line, sagging neck skin (&quot;turkey neck&quot;), wrinkles and fine lines, and lack of definition in the lips. Around the eyes, Therma CPT plus can treat under eye bags, hooding, rough texture on the eyelids, and other contributors to tired looking eyes. Elsewhere on the body, Therma CPT plus can treat wrinkled, crepey, sagging or bulging skin. For more information, please visit Therma CPT plus and You.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Where can I get a Therma CPT plus procedure?</span></strong><br />\nPhysicians all around the world are offering Therma CPT plus procedures. To find a Therma CPT plus practitioner near you, use the &quot;Find A Doctor&quot; feature on this site.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">How many treatments will I need?</span></strong><br />\nUnlike many other procedures, Therma CPT plus treatment delivers results in a single treatment for most patients. In fact, when it comes to skin tightening and contouring with little to no downtime, Therma CPT plus is one of the only non-invasive treatment procedures on the market.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">How long is the treatment?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus treatments average about 45 minutes for the face and up to 90 minutes for other parts of the body, depending on the size, location and condition of the area to be treated. Since Therma CPT plus is a short procedure and a single treatment, it fits into your busy lifestyle.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Is there any special preparation or follow-up?</span></strong><br />\nNo. Unlike surgery, there is no pre-procedure preparation such as blood work or fasting. And there is no special care required after treatment, aside from basic skin maintenance and sunscreens as part of a regular skincare regimen. Since the Therma CPT plus procedure has little to no downtime, most patients return to their regular activities immediately following treatment. Some patients exhibit a temporary redness or minor swelling after treatment, but this usually goes away within 24 hours.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">How does Therma CPT plus treatment work?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus uses radiofrequency technology to heat the deep, collagen rich layers of your skin. The heat helps tighten existing collagen and stimulate the formation of new collagen, which reduces sagging, renews contours, and improves the smoothness and texture of the skin&#39;s surface. For more information, please visit Therma CPT plus Science.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">How is Therma CPT plus technology different from other tightening procedures? </span></strong><br />\nUnlike some other procedures, Therma CPT plus involves no surgery, no injections and little to no downtime, and Therma CPT plus works on all skin types on and off the face. While laser treatments and other radiofrequency procedures also tighten skin, no other treatment heats as deeply as Therma CPT plus. By heating the innermost layers of skin, Therma CPT plus is the most effective at tightening collagen and stimulating the formation of new collagen, which results in tighter skin and an overall younger looking appearance.</p>\n\n<h3>Therma CPT plus vs. Other</h3>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">How do Therma CPT plus results compare with those of other treatments? </span></strong><br />\nSome people want the dramatic results of surgery. Others want the more subtle, gradual results of a non-invasive treatment with no downtime. This is where Therma CPT plus succeeds, delivering improved skin tone, texture and tightness. When lotions and potions are not enough and surgery is too much, Therma CPT plus is a safe, effective solution.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">When do the results appear, and how long do they last?</span></strong><br />\nVisible results may be immediate, and they may appear over time in the course of your body?s natural collagen rebuilding process. For most patients, measurable tightening and contouring appear gradually in the two to six months following a single treatment session. Results can last years depending on your skin condition and aging process.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">What does the Therma CPT plus procedure feel like?</span></strong><br />\nEach time the treatment device touches your skin, you&#39;ll feel a brief cooling sensation, followed by a deep but brief heating sensation, followed by another cooling sensation. The heating sensation is a sign that the deep layers of your skin are reaching effective temperatures for tightening. If your doctor has the latest Therma CPT plus technology you&#39;ll also feel a gentle vibration sensation for added patient comfort. Throughout the procedure, your physician will ask for feedback on the level of heat sensation to help balance your comfort with maximum results.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">What indications does Therma CPT plus have?</span></strong><br />\nTherma CPT plus is indicated for the non-invasive treatment of wrinkles and temporary improvement in the appearance of cellulite. In addition, Therma CPT plus is the first and only system to receive FDA clearance for non-invasive eyelid treatments.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(227,52,'postMenuLabel','id','Recover Your Youth (Therma CPTplus)',NULL),(228,52,'postMenuLabel','en','Recover Your Youth (Therma CPTplus)',NULL),(229,53,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | BB plus+</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.bbl01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"face-tite\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.sciton.jpg\" /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/BTGjGBzFgIM\" width=\"460\"></iframe></div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">BB plus+</h2>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Efektif, Serba Guna dan Kuat</span></strong><br />\nBroadBand Light (BBL) memberikan kesempatan kepada para dokter untuk menyediakan serangkaian prosedur estetika dalam suatu sistem yang sederhana. Sistem yang paling lengkap dan serbaguna, BBL hadir sebagai bagian dari Sciton&#39;s JOULE&trade; atau sebagai sistem terpisah.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Serangkaian Prosedur Estetika</span></strong><br />\nBBL merupakan pilihan sempurna yang menyediakan serangkaian perawatan termasuk <em>permanent hair reduction, acne reduction, dermal rejuvenation, microvasculature reduction, dan benign pigmented dan vascular lesion reduction.</em></p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Dapat Diprediksi dan Konsisten</span></strong><br />\nPenyempurnaan kulit yang signifikan dapat dicapai dengan teknik BBL yang tidak dilakukan tanpa operasi. Hasil klinis yang konsisten dan dapat diulang membuat BBL menjadi perawatan estetika yang sangat digemari.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Perawatan yang Dapat Disesuaikan &amp; Hasil yang Nyata</span></strong><br />\nDengan rangkaian panjang gelombang yang luas, dokter dapat menyediakan perawatan yang sesuai dengan kebutuhan tiap-tiap pasien. BBL membutuhkan lebih sedikit perawatan untuk mencapai hasil yang nyata dan lebih baik dibandingkan dengan system IPL lainnya.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Perawatan Tambahan &ndash; Pengencangan Kulit</span></strong><br />\nSkinTyte&trade; dapat ditambahkan sebagai perawatan terpisah ke dalam system BBL. Perawatan ini menggunakan energi sinar inframerah untuk memanaskan kolagen guna memperbarui pembentukan kolagen den meningkatkan kekencangan kulit.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Cepat dan Terjangkau</span></strong><br />\nBBL merupakan perawatan <em>phototherapy</em> yang tercepat dan paling ekonomis di pasaran.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Cepat</span></strong><br />\nDengan titik berukuran 15 x 45 mm dan tingkat pengulangan yang cepat, satu dokter dapat merawat beberapa pasien dalam waktu yang lebih singkat dengan <em>Skin Tyte</em> dan BBL. Untuk bagian-bagian yang lebih kecil, <em>Finesse Adapters</em> yang menempel secara magnetis akan meningkatkan fleksibilitas perawatan.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Tanpa Consumables (Barang Habis Pakai)</span></strong><br />\nBBL tidak menggunakan barang habis pakai sehingga tidak memerlukan biaya tambahan untuk mengganti <em>filter</em> dan <em>handpiece.</em></p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Hasil yang Sangat Baik, Konsisten &amp; Dapat Diprediksi</span></strong><br />\nPemanasan yang merata membidik bagian yang diinginkan secara mendalam dan efektif, merangsang pembentukan dan pemadatan kolagen secara langsung, dengan hasil yang sangat baik, konsisten, dan dapat diprediksi.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Aman dan Mudah Digunakan</span></strong><br />\nTeknologi lampu flash ganda, <em>Smart Filters, Finesse Adapters</em> dan pendinginan thermoelektrik yang revolusioner membuat BBL aman dan mudah digunakan oleh para dokter.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Pendinginan yang Kuat</span></strong><br />\nBBL menggunalan kristal safir yang tergabung dengan pendinginan thermoelektrik untuk menjaga area perawatan yang aman dan sejuk dengan suhu yang berkisar antara 0&deg;C hingga 30&deg;C.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Smart Filters yang Dapat Berganti</span></strong><br />\nSmart Filter yang dapat berganti memberikan perawatan untuk bermacam-macam kondisi kulit dengan panjang gelombang yang bervariasi tanpa interupsi.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Finesse Adapters</span></strong><br />\n<em>Finesse Adapter</em> yang menempel secara magnetis memudahkan para dokter untuk merawat area yang susah dijangkau dan berbagai struktur wajah. Tersedia dalam tiga ukuran yang berbeda.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Mudah Digunakan</span></strong><br />\nLampu ganda dengan sinyal broadband</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Mengatur Parameter dengan Touch Screen</span></strong><br />\nLampu Twin Flash yang tahan lama</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Skin Tyte untuk Pasien Anda:</span></strong><br />\nDengan Skin Tyte, Anda dapat memberikan prosedur yang nyaman dan sesuai permintaan tanpa efek samping.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">&bull; Proses Pendinginan yang Kuat untuk Kenyamanan Maksimal</span></strong><br />\nProses pendinginan yang tepat dengan Skin Tyte untuk memaksimalkan kenyamanan dan keamanan selama perawatan. Hanya BBL yang dapat mendinginkan permukaan kulit dengan suhu yang tepat dari 0&deg;C ke 30&deg;C.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">&bull; Aman untuk Semua Jenis Kulit</span></strong><br />\nSkin Tyte aman untuk pasien berkulit terang dan gelap yang tertarik untuk melakukan pengencangan kulit.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">&bull; Tanpa Efek Samping</span></strong><br />\nPasien dapat melanjutkan kegiatan mereka langsung setelah menjalani perawatan.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(230,53,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | BB plus+</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.bbl01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"face-tite\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.sciton.jpg\" /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/BTGjGBzFgIM\" width=\"460\"></iframe></div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">BB plus+</h2>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Effective, Versatile and Powerful</span></strong><br />\nBroadBand Light (BBL) gives physicians the opportunity to provide a broad range of aesthetic procedures in a simple system. The most complete and versatile broadband light system in its class, BBL comes as part of Sciton&#39;s JOULE&trade; platform or as a standalone system, BBL s.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Broad Range of Aesthetic Procedures</span></strong><br />\nBBLs BroadBand Light is the perfect choice for a broad range of treatments including permanent hair reduction, acne reduction, dermal rejuvenation,microvasculature reduction, and benign pigmented and vascular lesion reduction.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Predictable &amp; Consistent</span></strong><br />\nSignificant skin improvement can be achieved non-invasively with the BBL s. Consistent and reproducible clinical results make the BBL s a highly desired part of aesthetic practices.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Personalized Treatment &amp; Visible Results</span></strong><br />\nWith the broadest range of wavelengths, physicians can personalize treatments to fit each patient&#39;s needs. BBLs requires fewer treatments to achieve visible and superior results than other IPL systems.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Treatment Expansion - Skin Firming</span></strong><br />\nSkinTyte&trade; can be added as a separate module to the BBL s system. It employs infrared light energy to deeply heat dermal collagen leading to a renewed collagen foundation and increased skin firmness.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Fast and Cost Effective</span></strong><br />\nBBLs delivers the fastest and most economical phototherapy treatment on the market.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Fast</span></strong><br />\nWith a large 15 x 45 mm spot size and a rapid repetition rate, one can treat more patients in less time with the SkinTyte and BBLs For those smaller areas, magnetically attached Finesse Adapters provide added treatment flexibility.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">No Consumables</span></strong><br />\nBBL has no consumables which eliminates the excessive cost of replacement handpieces and filters.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Excellent, Consistent &amp; Predictable Results</span></strong><br />\nUniform heating targets deeply and effectively to a desired area, immediately stimulating collagen remodeling and contraction. Excellent, Consistent &amp; Predictable Results</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Safe and User Friendly</span></strong><br />\nThe revolutionary dual flash lamp technology, Smart Filters, Finesse Adapters, and precision thermoelectric cooling make BBLs safe and easy to use for physicians.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Powerful Cooling</span></strong><br />\nBBLs employs an integrated, thermoelectrically cooled, sapphire crystal that keeps the treatment area consistently safe and cool with precise temperatures from 0&deg;C . 30&deg;C.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Interchangeable Smart Filters</span></strong><br />\nRapidly interchangeable, on-the-fly Smart Filters, enables treatment of multiple skin conditions with various wavelengths without interruption.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Finesse Adapters</span></strong><br />\nMagnetically attached Finesse Adapters allow physicians to treat hard-to-reach areas and different facial structures. Available in three convenient sizes.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Easy to Use</span></strong><br />\nDual lamp broadband pulsed source</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Adjust parameter setting by touching the screen</span></strong><br />\nTwin Flash lamp has long lamp life</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">SkinTyte For Your Patients:</span></strong><br />\nWith the SkinTyte, you can offer your patients a highly requested, comfortable procedure with no downtime.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">&bull; Powerful Cooling for Maximum Comfort</span></strong><br />\nPrecision cooling with SkinTyte maximizes comfort and safety throughout the treatment. Only the BBL can cool the skin&#39;s surface to precise temperatures from 0&deg;C to 30&deg;C.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">&bull; Safe for All Skin Types</span></strong><br />\nSkinTyte is safe for light and dark skinned patients who are interested in improving skin firmness.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">&bull; No Downtime</span></strong><br />\nPatients are able to resume their regular activity immediately after with no visible signs of treatment.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(231,53,'postMenuLabel','id','Simply Stunning (BBLplus)',NULL),(232,53,'postMenuLabel','en','Simply Stunning (BBLplus)',NULL),(233,54,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"top\">\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"../lifting\">Lifting</a> | Face Tite (NON-Surgical Facial Reconstruction)</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end #top-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite01.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"picNav\">\r\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"sensual-lift\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"right-460\">\r\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Face Tite</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"big\">The Industry&#39;s Most Advanced Facial Contouring &amp; Refinement Procedure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Over time, the impact of the environment and genetics may diminish the youthful appearance of your face. FaceTite and NeckTite are effective procedures for addressing issues of local deposits of fat while simultaneously recontouring and tightening the chin, cheeks and jowl regions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FaceTite and NeckTite can provide a non-excisional solution previously only obtained through invasive surgical procedures (such as a facelift). By avoiding the complexities of more extensive surgery, you can benefit from a more rapid recovery with results that reflect a more natural appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHAT IS NECKTITE?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>NeckTite is a treatment that gently melts and suctions excess fat in small to medium sized areas. Gentle and deep heating will lead to contraction of the skin to re-contour the treatment area. These areas may include the neck, upper arms or inner thighs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHAT IS FACETITE?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>FaceTite can be a good solution that addresses lax skin in small localized areas. FaceTite can be a good solution where there is saggy skin that requires tightening and contouring, without the need for fat removal. These areas may include saggy skin and laxity around the eyes, eyebrows, forehead and mouth.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>DO FACETITE AND NECKTITE HAVE TO BE USED IN COMBINATION?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on your aesthetic concerns your cosmetic physician may elect to use either treatment in isolation, or in combination.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>HOW IS THIS BETTER THAN TRADITIONAL LIPOSUCTION?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Liposuction of the neck region can leave the treatment area looking worse if the skin is too lax, resulting in a &quot;turkey neck&quot; appearance. Patients may have better results using NeckTite or FaceTite as the heat energy will tighten the area compared to liposuction alone.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>HOW IS THIS BETTER THAN A FACELIFT?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>By avoiding a facelift excisional procedure, patients can benefit from reduced post-procedural swelling and discomfort. This is a less traumatic process with a more natural appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHAT KIND OF PROCEDURE CARE IS REQUIRED?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>FaceTite and NeckTite are minimally-invasive procedures performed under local anesthesia or light sedation. Post procedure, you can go home and resume your routine shortly after. Wearing a compression garment is required.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>HOW QUICKLY WILL I SEE RESULTS?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Results can be seen immediately, with best results noticeable after 6-12 weeks.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHAT TECHNOLOGY IS USED?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>These procedures use radio-frequency assisted lipolysis (RFAL) technology that thermally attacks subcutaneous fat and tightens collageneous tissue. RFAL technology is featured on the BodyTite platform. BodyTite and RFAL can also be used for treatment of the abdomen, hips, buttocks, thighs, knees, upper arms and other areas of fat deposits that require tightening. Your cosmetic physician can work with you to develop an appropriate RFAL solution to address all your problem areas.</p>\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite02.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"logoHair\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.surgeons.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n',NULL),(234,54,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"top\">\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"../lifting\">Lifting</a> | Face Tite (NON-Surgical Facial Reconstruction)</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end #top-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.facetite01.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"picNav\">\r\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"sensual-lift\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"right-460\">\r\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Face Tite</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"big\">The Industry&#39;s Most Advanced Fa