end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.skinlifting01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"botox\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"filler\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Lifting Botox Skin</h2>\n\n<p>Skin Lifting Botox an advance and unique technique specially designed to treat wrinkles and MicroVolume folds. Under dermatologist&#39;s care, very small amount of Botox are precisely injected into specific muscle lines, eliminating the risk to cause unnatural stretch or restrain on other facial spots. Skin Lifting Botox therapy targets specific small muscles and let the treatment works down to the lower skin layer. Therefore, patients would never experience a fake plastic feeling or unemotional face.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span class=\"ijo2\">Advantage</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Cause no effect to the ability to form facial expressions</li>\n	<li>Eliminate over-stretching sensation on face; flat out fine lines and wrinkles on face</li>\n	<li>Naturally lift your face to a perfect balance.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(259,60,'postMenuLabel','id','Lifting Botox Skin',NULL),(260,60,'postMenuLabel','en','Lifting Botox Skin',NULL),(261,61,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Filler</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.filler01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"skin-lifting-botox\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"natural-nose-lifting\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Filler</h2>\n\n<p>Kencangkan kulit Anda dan ciptakan dimensi yang sempurna melalui <em>Filler</em>, sebuah perawatan medis yang menggunakan bahan alami yang berasal dari tubuh manusia, yaitu kolagen. Dengan komponen yang berasal dari tubuh manusia, perawatan ini tidak berbahaya dalam menjaga kelembapan kulit, menyamarkan garis senyum, serta mengisi kekosongan di area bawah mata dan pipi, agar terlihat lebih muda. Hal yang terbaik dari perawatan ini adalah kemampuannya untuk memperbaiki tampilan wajah di bagian tertentu, seperti hidung atau dagu. Ahli bedah kami yang professional dapat memberikan hasil perawatan yang instan melalui perencanaan desain wajah yang unik dan halus. Efeknya bertahan selama 6-8 bulan, dengan <em>filler</em> yang melebur secara alami, tanpa meninggalkan residu sehingga Anda dapat menerima perawatan tambahan sesering mungkin.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Menyamarkan garis dan mengisi kekosongan di bawah mata dan pipi</li>\n	<li>Melembutkan bekas jerawat yang kasar</li>\n	<li>Membuat bibir tampak lebih penuh</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(262,61,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Filler</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.filler01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"skin-lifting-botox\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"natural-nose-lifting\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Filler</h2>\n\n<p>Puff up your skin and create dimension to its perfection with filler a medical treatment derived from the body&#39;s own natural substance, collagen. With human based component, the treatment yields no danger but helps lock up water in the skin, fills up Marionette?s lines, and restore lost volume under eyes and cheek area for a more youthful appearance. Best thing about it, filler takes the results to the next level with its ability to create facial dimensions by enhancing specific spots on your face e.g. nose or chin. Our professional surgeons offer an instant result of enhancement under their unique and delicate facial design plan. The effect lasts between 6-8 months and the filler dissolves naturally, leaving no trace of residues and enables you to receive further treatment as often as you can.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Fill lines and replenish lost volume under eyes and cheek area</li>\n	<li>Plump acne scar</li>\n	<li>Add fullness to the lips</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(263,61,'postMenuLabel','id','Filler',NULL),(264,61,'postMenuLabel','en','Filler',NULL),(265,62,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Natural Nose Lifting</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.nose01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"filler\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"specific-area-correction\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Natural Nose Lifting</h2>\n\n<p>Sebuah cara baru untuk memancungkan hidung Anda disebut HIKO: &ldquo;Hiko&rdquo; berasal dari kata &ldquo;Hi&rdquo; yang berarti &ldquo;tinggi&rdquo; dan &ldquo;Ko&rdquo; berarti &ldquo;hidung&rdquo; dalam bahasa Korea. Jadi, istilah &ldquo;Hiko&rdquo; mempunyai arti &ldquo;untuk memancungkan hidung&rdquo;. Di Thailand, dua pertiga wanita yang telah menjalani operasi hidung harus menjalani operasi tambahan untuk pembentukan hidung. Mereka harus mengalami rasa sakit, bengkak dan luka di bagian ujung hidung mereka, dan yang paling parah, adanya resiko kebutaan. HIKO <em>Nose Lifting</em> adalah salah satu solusi tanpa sayatan yang dapat memperbaiki penampilan Anda dengan bentuk wajah yang sempurna. Hiko <em>Nose Lifting</em> menggunakan benang tipis yang dapat diserap untuk mengangkat hidung dengan lembut hingga pada level yang diinginkan. Para pasien dapat melihat proses pemancungan hidung mereka, sebelum benar-benar menyetujui hasilnya dengan memasukkan silikon pada akhir proses. Hiko <em>Nose Lifting</em> memberi Anda kebebasan untuk mendesain bentuk hidung yang paling cocok untuk Anda dan memberikan penampilan terbaik bagi Anda.</p>\n\n<p>Jahitan yang dibuat pada proses Hiko <em>Nose Lifting</em> akan mengencangkan jaringan selaput tulang untuk mengumpulkan jaringan-jaringan di bawahnya dan menahannya pada posisi yang diinginkan. Setelah benang jahitan dilepas, selain mendapatkan efek &lsquo;menahan&rsquo;, produksi kolagen alami juga terangsang. Prosedur Hiko <em>Nose Lifting</em> hanya berlangsung sekitar 30 menit dan dapat dilakukan dibawah bius lokal. Prosedur ini merupakan pilihan tanpa sayatan yang bisa menambah dimensi alami wajah Anda dan mengubah hidung Anda menjadi sempurna. Proses penyembuhannya tidak akan menyebabkan kedua alis membengkok secara tidak alami. Para pasien dapat kembali bekerja setalah melakukan prosedur ini karena tidak adanya bekas luka setelah operasi.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Menyamarkan garis dan mengisi kekosongan di bawah mata dan pipi</li>\n	<li>Melembutkan bekas jerawat yang kasar</li>\n	<li>Membuat bibir tampak lebih penuh</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(266,62,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Natural Nose Lifting</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.nose01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"filler\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"specific-area-correction\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Natural Nose Lifting</h2>\n\n<p>A new way of lifting the nose to your most attractive self HIKO : &quot;Hiko&quot; comes from the word &quot;Hi&quot; in Korean meaning &quot;high&quot; and &quot;Ko&quot; meaning &quot;nose&quot;. Therefore, the term &quot;Hiko&quot; literally means &quot;to lift the nose&quot;. In Thailand, two third of the women who underwent a nose surgery have to go back for another operation for reshaping. They have to experience pain, swelling and bruising on their nose tip, and worst, a possible risk of being blind. HIKO Nose Lifting is one of the non-invasive solutions that can enhance your appearance to the perfect face dimensions. With Hiko Nose Lifting, thin absorbable threads are used to gently lift the nose to the desired level. Patients can see their nose being reshaped, before approving the result with silicone insertion. Hiko Nose lifting lets you design the shape and profile of the nose that is most suitable for you and enable you to become your most attractive self.</p>\n\n<p>With Hiko Nose Lifting, the suture anchors themselves to periosteum or fibrous membrane to gather the underlying tissues and secure them in the desired position. After the thread dissolves, not only the holding effect remains, but the natural collagen production is also stimulated. Hiko Nose Lifting takes only about 30 minutes and can be performed under local anesthesia on specific spot. It&#39;s a non-invasive option that could add natural dimension to your face and shift your nose to its perfection. The wound contracture doesn&#39;t offer enough resistance to force the brows to bend together in an unnatural way. Patient can be back to work after the treatment since there is no bruising and downtown to the surgery.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Fill lines and replenish lost volume under eyes and cheek area</li>\n	<li>Plump acne scar</li>\n	<li>Add fullness to the lips</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(267,62,'postMenuLabel','id','Natural Nose Lifting',NULL),(268,62,'postMenuLabel','en','Natural Nose Lifting',NULL),(269,63,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Pink Kiss</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.pinkkiss01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"filler\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"specific-area-correction\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Pink Kiss</h2>\n\n<p><span class=\"ijo2\">Kembalikan keremajaan warna bibir Anda</span></p>\n\n<p><em>Derma Crystal Q Laser</em> dapat merawat pudarnya warna bibir dan noda pada bibir tanpa mempengaruhi kulit normal di sekitarnya atau menyebabkan warna gelap. Laser ini dikembangkan secara khusus untuk diserap oleh pigmen gelap pada bibir sebelum menghancurkan melanin secara alami. Anda akan melihat bagaimana area berwarna gelap memudar secara bertahap. Dilengkapi dengan penggunaan <em>lip mask</em> yang mengandung bahan dasar makanan dan bahan tambahan, bibir Anda akan kembali tampak penuh dan halus dan secara bertahap akan berwarna kemerah-merahan.</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/symbol13.gif\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(270,63,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Pink Kiss</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.pinkkiss01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"filler\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"specific-area-correction\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Pink Kiss</h2>\n\n<p>Revive your lips to its school-girl youth Derma Crystal Q Laser provides a prominent ability to treat lips discoloration and lip blemish without irritating the surrounding normal skin or causing darkening color. The laser is specially developed to be absorbed by the dark pigmentation on the lips before naturally destroying the targeted skin melanin. You will experience a gradual fade of the darkening area. Together with lip mask that contains food and replenish substance, your lips will become plumping and smooth and gradually retrieve the same pinkish color.</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/symbol13.gif\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(271,63,'postMenuLabel','id','Pink Kiss',NULL),(272,63,'postMenuLabel','en','Pink Kiss',NULL),(273,64,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Specific Area Correction</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.correction01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"pink-kiss\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Specific Area Correction</h2>\n\n<p>Perawatan <em>Specific Area Correction</em> dirancang untuk memodifikasi dan memperbaiki bagian-bagian tertentu yang menjawab kebutuhan tiap-tiap orang.</p>\n\n<p>Bagian yang sering bermasalah:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Garis-garis pada dahi</li>\n	<li>&quot;Kaki gagak&quot; (kerutan di sudut luar mata)</li>\n	<li>Kantung mata</li>\n	<li>Pipi yang kendur atau bengkak</li>\n	<li>Garis senyum</li>\n	<li>Garis glabella (antara alis)</li>\n	<li><em>Indian fold</em> (lipatan mata)</li>\n	<li>Garis rahang yang tidak rata</li>\n	<li>Dagu terbelah</li>\n	<li><em>Stretch marks</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Bahan-bahan dan teknologi yang kami gunakan:</p>\n\n<p><em>Fine Thread</em> &ndash; teknik yang menggunakan benang dalam pola vector parallel dengan <em>Twin Fold</em></p>\n\n<p><em>Air Lifting</em> &ndash; suatu perawatan yang menggunakan udara yang diinjeksikan ke dalam lapisan kulit untuk menstimulasi proses restorasi kulit dan memperbaiki struktur kulit, <em>Platelet Rich Plasma (PRP)</em>; menyegarkan kulit secara efektif dengan mengaktifkan sel kulit dan <em>Platelet Derived Growth Factor.</em></p>\n\n<p><em>Botox</em> &ndash; mengurangi kerutan dan garis-garis halus pada wajah yang disebabkan oleh kontraksi otot wajah.</p>\n\n<p>Substansi Anti-Oksidan yang membantu melindungi sel-sel dalam melawan radikal bebas dan menghentikan proses oksidasi yang menghasilkan radikal bebas yang dapat menghancurkan sel-sel dalam tubuh.</p>\n\n<p><em>IRD (Inner RF Dissection)</em> atau <em>InnoFill</em> adalah teknologi yang mengirimkan energi dari Radio Frequency melalui <em>Cannula</em> ke dalam kulit. Perawatan ini memperbaiki garis senyum, merangsang produksi kolagen pada bagian tertentu, dan mengisi kekosongan pada wajah.</p>\n\n<p><em>Firexel</em> &ndash; sinar laser yang secara efektif mengaktifkan pengelupasan yang cukup mendalam namun tanpa iritasi; merangsang produksi kolagen dalam lapisan kulit tanpa menghancurkan lapisan luar kulit.</p>\n\n<p><em>AAD (Advanced Adipose Dispersion)</em> &ndash; teknologi yang menghilangkan sel-sel lemak; merangsang tubuh untuk membakar tumpukan lemak atau selulit.</p>\n\n<p><em>Der Signature</em> &ndash; teknologi yang menjaga unsur-unsur bergizi pada kulit, meningkatkan kesehatan kulit, dan mengisi kekosongan wajah.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(274,64,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Specific Area Correction</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Derma Cosmetic\" src=\"/assets/images/title.derma.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.correction01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"pink-kiss\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Specific Area Correction</h2>\n\n<p>Specific Area correction Treatment is designed to modifies and correct specific spots that answer each person&#39;s needs.</p>\n\n<p>Frequent problems are such as</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Forehead lines</li>\n	<li>Crow&#39;s feet</li>\n	<li>Eye bags</li>\n	<li>Sagging/puffy Cheek</li>\n	<li>Marionette?s lines / Nasojugal line</li>\n	<li>Glabella lines</li>\n	<li>Indian fold</li>\n	<li>Undefined Jawline</li>\n	<li>Double chin</li>\n	<li>Stretch marks</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Materials and technologies we use:</p>\n\n<p>Fine Thread a technique of applying the thread in a parallel vector pattern with Twin Fold</p>\n\n<p>Air Lifting a treatment using air injected into dermis in order to stimulate skin restoration process and adjust skin structure, Platelet Rich Plasma (PRP); effectively restore the skin by activating skin cell and Platelet Derived Growth Factor.</p>\n\n<p>Botox reduce wrinkles and lines caused by facial muscle contractions.</p>\n\n<p>Anti - Oxidant substances that help protect the cells against free radicals and stop oxidation process which generates the free radicals that damage the cells</p>\n\n<p>IRD (Inner RF Dissection) or InnoFill is a technology of delivering energy from Radio Frequency through a blunt Cannula into the skin. The treatment fixes deep frown lines, stimulates collagen production on specific spot, and lift the lost volume in the face.</p>\n\n<p>Firexel a laser beam that effectively executes a deep yet non-irritating exfoliation; stimulate collagen production in dermis without destroying the outer skin layer.</p>\n\n<p>AAD (Advanced Adipose Dispersion) a technology of eliminating fat cells; stimulate the body to burn accumulated fat deposits or cellulite.</p>\n\n<p>Der Signature a technology of locking up skin nourishing ingredient, strengthening skin health, and puff up the lost volume.</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/symbol12.gif\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(275,64,'postMenuLabel','id','Specific Area Correction',NULL),(276,64,'postMenuLabel','en','Specific Area Correction',NULL),(277,65,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Body</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/body-tite-rfal\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.rfal.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/lipo-selection-plus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.vaser.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair last\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.ultra.jpg\" usemap=\"mapmap20\" /><map id=\"mapmap20\" name=\"mapmap20\"><area alt=\"\" coords=\"10,92,89,112\" href=\"body/reshaping\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /> <area alt=\"\" coords=\"9,115,157,135\" href=\"body/tripolar\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /> <area alt=\"\" coords=\"8,137,100,157\" href=\"body/polagen\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /> <area alt=\"\" coords=\"9,155,101,175\" href=\"body/panashape\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /></map></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/fatfreeze\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.fatfreeze.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/sliming\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.slim.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(278,65,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic\">Derma Cosmetic</a> | Body</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/body-tite-rfal\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.rfal.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/lipo-selection-plus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.vaser.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair last\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.ultra.jpg\" usemap=\"mapmap20\" /><map id=\"mapmap20\" name=\"mapmap20\"><area alt=\"\" coords=\"10,92,89,112\" href=\"body/reshaping\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /> <area alt=\"\" coords=\"9,115,157,135\" href=\"body/tripolar\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /> <area alt=\"\" coords=\"8,137,100,157\" href=\"body/polagen\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /> <area alt=\"\" coords=\"9,155,101,175\" href=\"body/panashape\" shape=\"rect\" title=\"\" /></map></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/fatfreeze\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.fatfreeze.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"holder-hair\"><a href=\"body/sliming\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/thumb.slim.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(279,65,'postMenuLabel','id','Body',NULL),(280,65,'postMenuLabel','en','Body',NULL),(281,66,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic-body\">Body</a> | Liposuction</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.liposuction01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"lipo-selection-plus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Liposuction</h2>\n\n<p class=\"big\">RFAL (Radio Frequency Assisted Lipo Tightening):</p>\n\n<p><strong>Reduce, Tighten &amp; Shape</strong></p>\n\n<p>Banyak pria dan wanita memilih untuk melakukan liposuction guna mengurangi tumpukan lemak yang sulit dihilangkan meskipun mereka telah menjaga pola makan dan berolahraga. Selain bisa dirasakan manfaatnya secara langsung, Liposuction juga memiliki hasil yang tahan lama. Hal ini terjadi karena lemak yang dihilangkan oleh liposuction tidak digantikan kembali oleh tubuh.</p>\n\n<p>RFAL adalah terobosan terbaru dalam prosedur pembentukan tubuh yang didesain untuk menghilangkan lemak-lemak membandel pada area perut, pinggul, pantat, paha, lutut, lengan bagian atas, punggung dan pada area lain dimana terjadi penumpukan lemak. RFAL juga dapat dikombinasikan dengan perawatan <em>tummy tuck, body lifts dan mini-facelifts.</em></p>\n\n<p>PROSEDUR<br />\nRFAL menggunakan teknologi terkini yang disebut dengan RFAL <em>(Radio Frequency Assisted Lipo Tightening)</em> untuk memberikan solusi aman, lembut dan canggih dalam mendapatkan lekuk tubuh yang Anda inginkan. Teknologi RFAL bekerja dengan mencairkan dan menghilangkan lemak berlebih secara lembut melalui sayatan kecil pada area yang tersembunyi. Pencairan lemak di tahap awal akan membantu mengurangi rasa trauma yang muncul saat proses penghilangan lemak, dan sangat banyak mengurangi rasa sakit, bengkak atau ketidaknyamanan yang timbul setelahnya. RFAL akan menyingkirkan tumpukan-tumpukan lemak dan memberikan garis tubuh yang lebih baik.</p>\n\n<p>BAGAIMANA RFAL BEKERJA DALAM MENGENCANGKAN TUBUH?<br />\nSalah satu keistimewaan dari RFAL adalah kemampuannya untuk memanaskan jaringan lunak yang disayat dengan aman dan tepat. Proses pemanasan yang lembut dan mendalam ini akan membuat tubuh semakin kencang.</p>\n\n<p>BAGAIMANA RFAL LEBIH UNGGUL DARIPADA LIPOSUCTION BIASA?<br />\nSeiring dengan bertambahnya usia dan berat badan, kulit Anda akan kehilangan kekenyalannya. Liposuction dapat menambah masalah dengan menjadikan area yang dirawat tampak kasar dan tidak beraturan. Pasien yang memiliki tumpukan lemak disertai kulit kendur dan/atau <em>stretch marks</em> akan mendapatkan hasil yang lebih baik melalui prosedur RFAL untuk mengencangkan tubuh mereka dan untuk mengurangi resiko masalah kulit yang timbul setelah melakukan liposuction. Bila dibandingkan dengan liposuction biasa, RFAL memberikan alternatif yang lebih aman, lebih lembut dan lebih sedikit trauma, dengan hasil yang merata dan biasanya dengan bekas luka dan rasa tidak nyaman yang minimal.</p>\n\n<p>LANGKAH-LANGKAH PERAWATAN APA SAJA YANG DIBUTUHKAN?<br />\nRFAL merupakan prosedur minim sayatan yang dilakukan di bawah pengaruh bius lokal atau bius ringan. Anda dapat pulang ke rumah dan menjalankan kegiatan sehari-hari sesaat setelah prosedur selesai. Anda akan diminta untuk menggunakan pakaian yang ketat dan dapat melakukan olah raga <em>high impact</em> dibawah pengawasan dokter.</p>\n\n<p><strong>RESULTS.</strong> Hasilnya dapat langsung terlihat; hasil terbaik tampak setelah 6-12 minggu.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(282,66,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic-body\">Body</a> | Liposuction</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.liposuction01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"lipo-selection-plus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Liposuction</h2>\n\n<p class=\"big\">RFAL (Radio Frequency Assisted Lipo Tightening):</p>\n\n<p><strong>Reduce, Tighten &amp; Shape<br />\nThe Industry&#39;s Most Advanced Body Refinement Procedure </strong></p>\n\n<p>Many men and women choose to have liposuction to help remove stubborn pockets of fat that are difficult to tone up even if your diet is healthy and you exercise regularly. Not only is it immediately effective, the fact that the fat cells removed by liposuction do not get replaced by your body, the results will be long-lasting as well.</p>\n\n<p>RFAL is a breakthrough body reshaping procedure designed to remove stubborn fat including abdomen, hips, buttocks, thighs, knees, upper arms, back and other areas of fat deposits. It can also be a good combination treatment for tummy tucks, body lifts and mini-facelifts.</p>\n\n<p>PROCEDURE<br />\nRFAL uses an advanced technology called RFAL (Radio Frequency Assisted Lipo Tightening) to offer you a safe, gentle and sophisticated body contouring solution. RFAL technology gently melts and remove excess fat through a tiny incision in an inconspicuous location. By pre-melting the fat, the removal is a far less traumatic process, greatly reducing post-procedural pain, swelling or discomfort. RFAL will eliminate fatty deposits and provide improvements to re-contour your body.</p>\n\n<p>HOW DOES RFAL RESULT IN BODY TIGHTENING?<br />\nOne of the unique features of RFAL is its ability to safely and precisely heat the soft tissue being contoured. This gentle and deep heating will lead to body tightening.</p>\n\n<p>HOW IS THIS BETTER THAN TRADITIONAL LIPOSUCTION?<br />\nAs you age or gain weight, your skin becomes less elastic. Liposuction can compound the problem by leaving the treatment area looking lumpy or irregular. Patients with skin laxity and/or stretch marks along with fat deposits can have better results using RFAL to firm their body and decrease the risk of post-liposuction skin laxity. Compared to traditional liposuction, RFAL offers a safer, gentler and less traumatic alternative with more uniform results and usually minimal postoperative discomfort and bruising.</p>\n\n<p>WHAT KIND OF PROCEDURE CARE IS REQUIRED?<br />\nRFAL is a minimally invasive procedure performed under local anesthesia or light sedation. Post procedure, you can go home and resume your routine shortly after. You will be required to wear a compression garment and can resume high impact exercise upon the advice of your doctor.RESULTS Results can be seen immediately, with best results noticeable after 6-12 weeks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(283,66,'postMenuLabel','id','Body Tite RFAL (Radio frequency) Assisted Liposuction',NULL),(284,66,'postMenuLabel','en','Body Tite RFAL (Radio frequency) Assisted Liposuction',NULL),(285,67,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic-body\">Body</a> | Lipo Selection Plus</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.lipoplus01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"panashape\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"body-tite-rfal\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<p class=\"big\">It&#39;s your body</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Be Selective!</h2>\n\n<p>Bila Anda berpikir untuk melakukan perawatan kecantikan, Anda layak untuk mempertimbangkan teknik-teknik terbaru dan tercanggih.</p>\n\n<p>Your body, only better</p>\n\n<p>Apakah Lipo Selection Plus?<br />\nApa perbedaannya dibandingkan dengan liposuction biasa?</p>\n\n<p><strong>Lipo Selection plus</strong> merupakan prosedur minim sayatan untuk menghilangkan lemak tubuh yang tidak diinginkan secara tepat dan efisien. Dibandingkan dengan teknik liposuction yang kasar, Lipo Selection Plus menggunakan teknologi ultrasound yang modern yang didesain untuk membentuk tubuh Anda dengan lembut. Prosedur LipoSelection dapat membedakan jaringan lemak yang tertuju dengan jaringan-jaringan penting lainnya, seperti jaringan syaraf, pembuluh darah dan jaringan penghubung.</p>\n\n<p>Teknologi Lipo Selection Plus yang inovatif, memecah lemak sambil menjaga jaringan-jaringan penting lainnya. Hanya prosedur LipoSelection yang menggunakan cara kerja Lipo Selection plus dengan mencairkan lemak dan kemudian menyingkirkannya dari dalam tubuh untuk hasil yang lebih halus dan proses penyembuhan yang tepat dengan rasa sakit seminim mungkin.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Apa yang terjadi saat proses Lipo Selection plus berlangsung?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Pada awalnya, area yang dituju diisi dengan larutan garam khusus untuk memberikan efek mati rasa dan mengecilkan pembuluh darah (untuk meminimalisir kehilangan darah dan mengurangi luka). Larutan ini membasahi dan mengisi area yang dituju, sehingga proses pemecahan jaringan lemak menjadi lebih mudah dengan energi ultrasonik dari sistem Lipo Selection plus.</p>\n\n<p>Kemudian, sebuah <em>probe</em> kecil yang mengeluarkan energi suara (mirip dengan yang digunakan untuk menghilangkan katarak pada mata) digunakan untuk memecah jaringan lemak yang dituju tanpa merusak jaringan-jaringan penting lainnya. Akhirnya, lemak yang dicairkan, disingkirkan melalui proses sedot yang lembut yang dirancang untuk meminimalisir kerusakan jaringan-jaringan di sekitarnya.</p>\n\n<p><strong>&ldquo;Rasa percaya diri saya meningkat dengan pesat- tidak ada ungkapan yang lebih tepat untuk menjelaskan perasaan nyaman ini ketika kau menyingkirkan sesuatu yang tidak kau sukai dari tubuhmu.&rdquo;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Karena terkadang, walaupun kau sudah berusaha keras, lemak itu tetap tidak menghilang...</strong></p>\n\n<p>Setiap orang memiliki bentuk dan ukuran tubuh yang berbeda-beda. Setiap jenis bentuk tubuh memiliki bagian dengan tumpukan lemak dan, meski dengan diet dan olah raga yang ketat, tonjolan lemak yang tidak diinginkan itu tetap ada. Teknologi Lipo Selection plus yang sudah dipatenkan dan teknik LipoSelection&reg; yang terkini menawarkan pilihan aman bagi Anda yang ingin menyingkirkan tumpukan lemak membandel dengan memberikan bentuk tubuh yang lebih indah dengan pemulihan cepat.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Apakah Lipo Selection plus pilihan tepat bagi saya?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Bila Anda merasa frustasi dengan bagian-bagian tubuh tertentu yang tidak berubah meski telah melakukan diet dan olah raga, Lipo Selection plus dapat memberikan jalan keluar. Jika Anda dalam kondisi sehat dan sedang mencari solusi cepat dengan sedikit rasa sakit untuk menghilangkan tumpukan lemak membandel, perawatan LipoSelection dapat menjadi jawabannya. Para pasien yang pernah mengatakan tidak pada liposuction sekarang menemukan bahwa prosedur LipoSelection adalah prosedur minim sayatan yang menjadi pilihan untuk mencapai bentuk tubuh idaman. Meskipun ada batasan-batasan terhadap banyaknya lemak yang bisa dihilangkan, dokter Anda dapat membantu Anda dalam berbagai keputusan mengenai bagian tubuh yang ingin dibentuk, hasil yang diinginkan, dan proses pemulihannya.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"logoHair\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.surgeons.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(286,67,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic-body\">Body</a> | Lipo Selection Plus</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.lipoplus01.jpg\" />\n<div class=\"picNav\">\n<div class=\"cta\"><a href=\"../contact-us\">Contact Us</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"prevnextHolder\"><a href=\"panashape\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.prev.gif\" /></a> <a href=\"body-tite-rfal\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/btn.next.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<p class=\"big\">It&#39;s your body</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Be Selective!</h2>\n\n<p>If you&#39;re thinking about a cosmetic procedure, you owe it to yourself to look at new and advanced techniques.</p>\n\n<p>Your body, only better</p>\n\n<p>What is Lipo Selection plus?<br />\nHow does it differ from traditional liposuction?</p>\n\n<p><strong>Lipo Selection plus</strong> is a minimally invasive procedure that precisely and efficiently removes unwanted body fat. An alternative to the harsh techniques of traditional liposuction, Lipo Selection plus uses state-of-the-art ultrasound technology designed to gently reshape your body. What distinguishes the LipoSelection procedure is its ability to differentiate targeted fat from other important tissues - such as nerves, blood vessels and connective tissue.</p>\n\n<p>Innovative Lipo Selection plus technology breaks up fat while conserving these other important tissues. Only the LipoSelection procedure uses the proprietary Lipo Selection plus System to first liquefy fat and then remove it from the body to promote smooth results and rapid healing with only low to minimal pain.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What happens during Lipo Selection plus?</strong></p>\n\n<p>First, the area to be reshaped is filled with a special saline solution that helps numb the site and shrink the blood vessels (to minimize blood loss and reduce bruising). This solution wets and fills the area to be treated, making it easier to break up fatty tissue with the Lipo Selection plus System&#39;s ultrasound energy.</p>\n\n<p>Then a small probe transmits sound energy (similar to that used for cataract removal from the eye) to fragment fatty tissue on contact while leaving other important tissues largely intact. Finally, the liquefied fat is removed through a gentle suction process designed to minimize damage to surrounding tissues.</p>\n\n<p><strong>&quot;My self-confidence has risen dramatically- there&#39;s just no describing how good it feels to get rid of that one thing you really dislike about your body.&quot;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Because sometimes no matter how hard you work, it just won?t go away...</strong></p>\n\n<p>People come in all different shapes and sizes. Every body type has areas that are predisposed to fat storage and, even with rigorous diet and exercise, those unwanted bulges often persist. Patented Lipo Selection plus technology and the advanced LipoSelection&reg; technique now offer a safe alternative for ridding yourself of those stubborn fat deposits to provide you a smooth new shape with fast recovery.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Is Lipo Selection plus right for me?</strong></p>\n\n<p>If you are frustrated by the resistance of certain body areas to diet and exercise, Lipo Selection plus can provide a solution. If you are healthy and seeking a fast, low-pain solution for losing stubborn fat deposits, the LipoSelection procedure could be your answer. Patients who say they would have never considered liposuction are now finding the LipoSelection procedure is a minimally invasive option for the achievement of their body reshaping goals. Although there are limits to the amount of fat that can be removed, your doctor can assist you with your decision about potential areas for contouring, anticipated results, and the recovery process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"logoHair\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/logo.surgeons.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',NULL),(287,67,'postMenuLabel','id','Lipo Selection Plus',NULL),(288,67,'postMenuLabel','en','Lipo Selection Plus',NULL),(289,68,'post','id','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic-body\">Body</a> | Panashape</div>\n\n<div id=\"pageTitle\"><img alt=\"Body Center\" src=\"/assets/images/title.body.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #top-->\n\n<div class=\"left-460\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/images/pic.adipo01.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"right-460\">\n<h2 class=\"greylarge2\">Panashape</h2>\n\n<p><span class=\"ijo2\">Mengurangi Lemak dan Mengencangkan Kulit</span></p>\n\n<p>Perawatan PANASHAPE menggunakan radiofrekuensi Monopolar dan Bipolar bersamaan dengan pijatan yang membantu mengurangi lemak yang menumpuk di bagian tertentu. Perawatan ini membantu menghancurkan sel-sel lemak menjadi partikel-partikel kecil dan membawanya ke sistem limfatik. PANASHAPE juga membantu melancarkan peredaran darah dan menyeimbangkan metabolisme dengan cara yang lebih efektif dibandingkan dengan olahraga biasa yang tidak bisa menyingkirkan selulit.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Tanpa operasi, tanpa rasa sakit, aman, dan tanpa luka</li>\n	<li>Mengatasi sindrom kulit jeruk, mengencangkan kulit, memperbaiki sistem peredaran darah, memberikan bentuk tubuh S untuk meningkatkan daya tarik Anda.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<!--end #container-->',NULL),(290,68,'post','en','<div id=\"container\">\n<div id=\"top\">\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\"><a class=\"backhome\" href=\"../index\">Home</a> | <a href=\"../derma-cosmetic\">Aesthetic</a> | <a href=\"derma-cosmetic-body\">Body</a> | Panashape</div>\